name: Aisha Patel
summary: Aisha Patel is a 28-year-old woman who works in the tech industry as a Software Engineer. She values family, mindfulness, and ambition. Aisha is interested in technology, traveling, and painting. Hailing from Atlanta, Georgia, Aisha currently lives in Los Angeles, California, and is looking for a long-term, monogamous relationship. She speaks English and Hindi and has a graduate-level education. Aisha follows Hindu religion and is politically liberal. She identifies as straight and uses She/Her/Hers pronouns. Aisha belongs to a South Asian ethnicity. She does not have children but wants to in the future. She does not smoke or drink, and she leads an active lifestyle. Her ideal partner would be a man between the ages of 28 to 35, who does not have children but is open to having them in the future, and leads an active, smoke-free, and alcohol-free lifestyle.
